Packages known to be needed to build in debian wheezy.
Some of these will pull in other ones.

    automake
    build-essential
    ccmake
    dssi-dev
    fluid
    libboost-dev
    libcairo2-dev
    libfftw3-dev
    libfltk1.3-dev
    libglu1-mesa-dev
    libjack-jackd2-dev
    libjpeg8-dev
    libxft-dev
    libxinerama-dev
    libxml2-dev
    pkg-config
    xutils-dev

Other distros may have slightly different names or versions,
and may even have these installed be default.
